name: Totally Fine Library
description:
Solve puzzles in the Totally Fine Library. Can you get all the books back on their shelves?

10 levels ranging from easy to moderate difficulty.

This puzzle was made as part of the thinky game jam 2021. The theme was "The Elephant in the Room"

WASD/Arrow to move. Z to undo. R to restart.
